latestIgtvVideos.title: The Joy of Gifting with Kama Ayurveda ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I love gifting my close people and picking the right gift is an effort. 

I choose Kama Ayurveda Gift Boxes as they an exquisite packaging and their products are filled with the goodness of Ayurveda. 

This gifting section has something for everyone, even the one’s who are difficult to please. (Gift Card, Yay) 

So here’s what I got – 
Rose Essentials for Her Gift Box which has skin & body products with a decadent fragrance of roses 
Face Care Box which has a face cleanser and pure toner 
Gardens of India Box which has 3 beautiful soaps 
Gift card 
A customised box with Suvarna Face Pack, Rose Water and Kokum Almond Body Butter 
Another customised box with Jwalini Oil, Rose Jasmine Body Cleanser & Conditioner.

@kamaayurveda
